<h1><span id="France_d.E2.80.99outre-mer"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="France_d’outre-mer">France d’outre-mer</span></h1></div><p><i><span style="font-size:small;">Autre région, par exemple dépendance, union, ancien pays</span></i>
</p><figure typeof="mw:File/Thumb"><a href="/wiki/File:France_in_the_World_(%2BAntarctica_claims).svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5f/France_in_the_World_%28%2BAntarctica_claims%29.svg/400px-France_in_the_World_%28%2BAntarctica_claims%29.svg.png" decoding="async" width="400" height="200" class="mw-file-element" srcset="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5f/France_in_the_World_%28%2BAntarctica_claims%29.svg/600px-France_in_the_World_%28%2BAntarctica_claims%29.svg.png 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5f/France_in_the_World_%28%2BAntarctica_claims%29.svg/800px-France_in_the_World_%28%2BAntarctica_claims%29.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="2521" data-file-height="1260" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
