<div class="transcludebox">Texte inclus de<br /><a href="/wiki/Commons:Copyright_rules_by_territory/Nauru/fr" title="Commons:Copyright rules by territory/Nauru/fr">COM:Nauru</a></div>
<h1><span class="mw-headline" id="Nauru">Nauru</span></h1></div>

<table class="infobox infobox-copyright-rules mw-content-ltr" lang="fr" dir="ltr" style="width:22em;width:280px;"><tbody><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center">
<div class="infobox-copyright-rules-title">Règles du droit d'auteur&#160;: Nauru</div><div class="infobox-copyright-rules-shortcut">Raccourci: COM:NAURU</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center">
<span class="mw-image-border" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Nauru.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img alt="Drapeau (Nauru)" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/30/Flag_of_Nauru.svg/100px-Flag_of_Nauru.svg.png" decoding="async" width="100" height="50" class="mw-file-element" srcset="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/30/Flag_of_Nauru.svg/150px-Flag_of_Nauru.svg.png 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/30/Flag_of_Nauru.svg/200px-Flag_of_Nauru.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="300" /></a></span></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center">
