<div class="transcludebox">Texte inclus de<br /><a href="/wiki/Commons:Copyright_rules_by_territory/Samoa/fr" title="Commons:Copyright rules by territory/Samoa/fr">COM:Samoa</a></div>
<h1><span class="mw-headline" id="Samoa">Samoa</span></h1></div>

<table class="infobox infobox-copyright-rules mw-content-ltr" lang="fr" dir="ltr" style="width:22em;width:280px;"><tbody><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center">
