<a href="/wiki/Template:PD-Samoa" title="Template:PD-Samoa"><span style="font-family:monospace,monospace;">&#123;&#123;PD-Samoa&#125;&#125;</span></a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="background:#ddf;text-align:left;font-weight:bold;font-size:smaller;"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-1_alpha-3" class="extiw" title="en:ISO 3166-1 alpha-3">ISO 3166-1 alpha-3</a></th><td style="font-size:smaller;">
