</li>
<li id="cite_note-Act1998-50"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="#cite_ref-Act1998_50-0">↑</a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://wipolex.wipo.int/en/legislation/details/13393">Copyright Act 1998 (as consolidated in 2011)</a>.&#32;Samoa&#32;(2011). Retrieved on <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2018-11-05">2018-11-05</span>.</span>
</li>
</ol></div>
