<li id="cite_note-Act2000-67"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="#cite_ref-Act2000_67-0">↑</a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://wipolex.wipo.int/en/legislation/details/10729">Copyright and Related Rights Act No. 42 of 2000</a>.&#32;Vanuatu&#32;(2011). Retrieved on <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2018-11-04">2018-11-04</span>.</span>
